(468, 'Aveli Paide', '2011-07-27 12:05:42', 'avelipaide@gmail.com', 'Tartu/ Estonia', '', 'HelloI was last year in Viljandi Folk festival and i really liked yourperformance. My father is also a very big fan of yours. He bought yourlast album "Жили-были" but he wanted your first album to. He saw at thefestival that one person bought the last album and he didn''t get it. Sohe really want your first album. I read from the news that you are mabye performing this summer in Estonia- is it true?? And were that is goingto take place. And when you are going to write back in this email youcan also write in russian because my father knows russian very good. One more question. Maybe in Peterburg somewere can by this your firstalbum? Do you know that somewhere can? Also my father looks forwards to your christmas CD and your next album.Greeting from Estonia Aveli'),
(469, 'bodhi', '2011-07-18 14:40:13', '', 'Ярославль', '', 'Ребята, огромное спасибо за вашу музыку, а главное за то, как вы кней бережно относитесь. Желаю вам дальнейших творческих успехов. Мытанцуем под вас:)'),
